    "kural": {
      "line1": "தவமும் தவமுடையார்க்கு ஆகும் அதனை",
      "line2": "அஃதிலார் மேற்கொள் வது."
    },
    "meaning": {
      "ta": "தவக்கோலமும் தவஒழுக்கமும் உடையவர்க்கே பொருந்துவதாகும்; அக் கோலத்தை தவஒழுக்கம் இல்லாதவர் மேற்கொள்வது வீண்முயற்சியாகும்.",
      "en": "Austerities can only be borne, and their benefits enjoyed, by those who have practised them (in a former birth); it will be useless for those who have not done so, to attempt to practise them (now)"
    },
    "couplet_en": "To 'penitents' sincere avails their 'penitence'; Where that is not, 'tis but a vain pretence",
    "transliteration": "Thavamum Thavamutaiyaarkku Aakum Adhanai Aqdhilaar Merkol Vadhu",
